name: ojc-show-printable-page
description: It displays the Printable Page based on the DIV identifier sent.

printElement.description: The component id of the DOM Element parent for printing. If not given the entire document will be used

forcePrint.description: If true, triggers the print automatically. By default is false

print.description: Programmatically invoke the print, can be used instead of pressing the button.

startIcon.description: Slot for optional start icon on the export button (if displayed)

endIcon.description: Slot for optional end icon on the export button (if displayed)
